更上過無綫節目《都市閒情》做嘉賓分享中醫知識。佢唔止學識淵博，仲好注重外表，熱愛做Gym，操得一身肌肉，仲經常喺網上晒肌，同Rei一樣郎才女貌，又鍾意做運動，唔怪得咁投契啦！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190120183411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190120183411&h=bc2f0200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190120183411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190120183411&h=e431ab28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190120183411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190120183411&h=6514ce0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190120183411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190120183411&h=540cf978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190120183411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120183213276-0120_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190120183411&h=d5299c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120183213276-012